Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是杀害了休斯准将的子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口径是45mm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只使用了一发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁不住想夸犯人枪法好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从近距离开的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是女性也可以办到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所使用的枪的口径是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,45mm口径
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的子弹补充申请
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里写着一发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用在哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在申请书上也写了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做爱德华·艾尔利克护卫的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第五研究所…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五研究所已经被封锁了 应该是没人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那时并非没人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的主张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去找使用了的子弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五研究所因为迷之爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了瓦砾之山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用枪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本应是没人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且即使想找子弹 也已经被埋在了瓦砾之下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:02:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 在作案时间前后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有证人说看到你从现场离开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天正在放假 我在父母家里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请向我的父母确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人以及亲密朋友的证言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法作为不在场证明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽亚·罗斯正在受审
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是长官也无法见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁斯军曹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少佐也来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 罗斯少尉的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 实际上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上在第五研究所为了艾尔利克兄弟的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也和少尉一起开了一枪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这件事情递交了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没被接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备把少尉弄成犯人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}冰冷的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看看 都是伤痕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常辛苦的旅程呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你希望我们怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们从没找我商量你们自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在休斯先生被杀的危险地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德和阿尔一直在战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一想 就觉得非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 说不定会死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然从我面前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像爸爸和妈妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一想就觉得非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话 想让你们放弃旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想让你们恢复原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也想让你们停止危险的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道想怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉真温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你在说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都很温柔的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 伤痕会变多的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（你在说什么呢 真是的）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 又是报纸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一整天都陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有这么点乐子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是法尔蔓准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从外线打的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请接通马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 代码是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么 这么紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Airam George Oliver 4649
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是那时的大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有咬尾蛇刺青的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吓我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在前台…报纸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽亚·罗斯少尉被断定为杀害休斯准将的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐或少佐也许知道点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是小狗的项圈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 再问你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是15岁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别骗人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是入侵者 快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖待着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没劲 没劲 没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有没有干劲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开 你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 不能砍就是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 枪不起作用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我从这里放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从清国来的非法入境者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 这么大老远跑来真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把我放出去我就帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间和你玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说哪个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东边的清国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗 甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第五研究所的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能记得真让我高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是每次看到右手被枪打的洞就会想起那时候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害休斯的大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报纸可是写着确定是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样下去肯定是被套上罪名接受枪决
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人 骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要仔细调查的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你选择吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是等着被乱枪射死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是和我一起逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二选一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此以外没有选择了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 爸爸 妈妈 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:10:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好做好护卫 你这个笨蛋骨头铠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 气势不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人就是要胆子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知市内全区
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽亚·罗斯越狱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎有凶恶的共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即抓捕归案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果抵抗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,允许射杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要多问 跑就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗斯少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连麟也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我要问的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那边的胡同里一直走就能逃到仓库街
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藉着那里的黑暗应该能逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗斯少尉 休斯中佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 宪兵来了的话 会被射杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗斯少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉 罗斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是玛丽亚·罗斯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了 一线眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…麟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么和那种家伙在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后再告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 钢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会被罗斯少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不告诉我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然对长官出手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掂量一下自己有几斤重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个家伙把罗斯少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗斯少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面有令 射杀越狱的玛丽亚·罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫仅此而已？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于隐瞒休斯之死的事情 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是别对命令提出异议
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得要求解释
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实地遵从
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是军队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请说明一下这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面应该有令 如果抵抗就可以射杀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为抵抗了 所以杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说准将是你的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让罗斯少尉越狱的不会是你的手下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了亲手烧死她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要主观地判断事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没把休斯准将的死讯告诉你们 真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全到齐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺克斯医生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,损伤实在太严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是从勉强留下的牙齿治疗痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以断定这个人是玛丽亚·罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是过份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个美人弄成了炭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你对她有很深的仇恨呢 马斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报了仇 满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到伊修瓦尔战的英雄会对一个小姑娘下这样的毒手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐 这次我的部下做了非常不该的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到罗斯少尉会杀人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个很诚实 很认真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有同情心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你是疲劳积累得太多了 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去休假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经住过东部 那里不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有都会的喧嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且美人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古漂亮地替挚友报了仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可喜可贺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:18:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了让大佐安分的作战吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗把饵吃了也是不错的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 他似乎引起了其他人的不满
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会被部下抛弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休假申请
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个时期吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然擅自出门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被发现了的话 不知道大佐会怎么教训我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来的时候没有被人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是被凶恶的犯人抓住的可怜军人 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 从刚才开始你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼烟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼烟？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 把不认识的人带来 你到底在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 真让我们好找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人变多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉莎白 还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你经常给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常偷懒的话会惹你那可怕的副官生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 她休假了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托这个福 我能往你那里打电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉休假后马上就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监护人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到了这里以后一直没有休假
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多想拿个假期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:19:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近迷上了钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你突然干什么 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 你的机械铠坏掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是重大事态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须马上修理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我负责把你送到利塞布尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回利塞布尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 阿尔 听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太显眼了 请留在中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 马上就准备火车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这也是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个男人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮少佐和爱德华·艾尔利克坐上火车了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来碍事的人就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见了拘留所袭击犯的目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是犯人的画像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和火焰之大佐有联系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 可能性很大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 他不仅逃得很快而且藏得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真无能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真烦人 大妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人手不够
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人手？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.55,0:22:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人手的话 有这个就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 该你出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刽子手巴利
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切的真实都在克塞鲁克塞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在渐渐腐朽消亡之城市的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,0:24:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拂拭了少年的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.66,0:24:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.29,0:24:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第十八话 渺小人类的傲慢手掌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.37,0:24:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类哟 升起反击的狼烟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:06.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:12.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:24.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:30.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:32.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:36.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:43.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:44.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:46.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:49.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:56.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:59.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:01.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:05.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:06.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:08.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:14.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:19.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:26.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:33.32,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:37.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:44.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:50.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:55.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:57.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.88,0:23:01.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:08.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:16.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:22.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:27.64,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:32.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,去搜寻星尘与光芒四射的永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.85,0:23:38.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 那天也许还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:44.16,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季节依然在不断地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:48.24,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有点迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:52.28,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:56.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}请让我维持到永远
